{"tid":1375254,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港女查身份證單野教識我地被check身證下嘅應對手法","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:29:57.000Z","uid":28451,"like":124,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"066d2983ad763ea29d2ed001fd3d29abe7e47eb3","tid":1375254,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"今次港女查身份證單野，話我地知，係鏡頭下佢絕對唔敢搞你，所以基本上要堅決唔俾未出示委任證嘅狗隻check身份證，或者冇律師在場下俾佢地check袋。要大大增加佢成本，唔好妥協，呢個人市民權利，亦係狗隻義務。<br />\n<br />\n咁如果去到一條友落單，暗角打鑊嘅地步，市民係冇計，呢啲自己執生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">基本流程</span><br />\n<br />\n1, 要求出示委任證，否則認為佢冒警<br />\n<br />\n2, 要求在場所有涉及查身份證嘅狗都出示委任證，否則認為佢地包庇人冒警<br />\n<br />\n3, 叫記者影晒佢地委任證<br />\n<br />\n4, 如果狗仲要check就俾身份證，check袋要拒絕，要求律師在場，理由係合理懷疑會俾人賊贓嫁禍"},{"pid":"9e6e8654393bc766c1e059ac97c3839bece7b65d","tid":1375254,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7279038ae34b7705f561addefa0d939dd0ebec","tid":1375254,"uid":282624,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"年輕人未出過社會<br />\n好多都不知所措又好驚<br />\n啲餓狗淨喺識揀啲老弱婦孺嚟搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15af6b262dc437cab0dad9e1a61c21db3a5fdb51","tid":1375254,"uid":28451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f7279038ae34b7705f561addefa0d939dd0ebec","tid":1375254,"uid":282624,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"年輕人未出過社會<br />\n好多都不知所措又好驚<br />\n啲餓狗淨喺識揀啲老弱婦孺嚟搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"所以要講俾佢地知"},{"pid":"8de29f5fd0a92b5a61d9f975f0103cd166efe681","tid":1375254,"uid":170309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"066d2983ad763ea29d2ed001fd3d29abe7e47eb3","tid":1375254,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,