9-07-28T04:33:10.000Z","msg":"【如果有記者】<br />\n咁你地係咪身有屎呀，無野怕咩show委任證"},{"pid":"e95ea66027a343c8bf9c9e1a67f22131ff905cf4","tid":1375254,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"關於回應鳩問題，可以參考我另一個post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n除左做文宣本身之外，仲可以提供答案，用黎回應藍絲親戚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"badb06fda40ea1b906204224fb672e727bb21ec3","tid":1375254,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d40cce255ba642b0b6d5a4a4a945161dc340e76","tid":1375254,"uid":53415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b634c52ea9f347b03e33bf8558263a9431cc7e","tid":1375254,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:31:36.000Z","msg":"然後好常聽到狗之後會咁講:  &quot;你係咪身有屎呀! 你無野怕咩check 袋呀?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住點回?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"我無野講?"},{"pid":"7e742091f187c2ba14a2080065e241a6d3978cc8","tid":1375254,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"如果佢有出示委任證,佢係有權CHECK你袋喎<br />\n佢地正常程序一定會喺你面前開你個袋睇或者拎D野出黎<br />\n你要等律師實會要你返差館等"},{"pid":"aa1b84e58303dff669f422aa835cf8789dc35df6","tid":1375254,"uid":207902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65b634c52ea9f347b03e33bf8558263a9431cc7e","tid":1375254,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:31:36.000Z","msg":"然後好常聽到狗之後會咁講:  &quot;你係咪身有屎呀! 你無野怕咩check 袋呀?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住點回?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim